## Part 3 — InstallState enum

```kotlin
enum class InstallState {
    INSTALLED,
    DOWNLOADING,
    NOT_INSTALLED,
    ERROR
}
```

Status chip behavior per state:
- `INSTALLED` → show chip, background = `gn_status_installed` (#00E5C3), text = "Installed"
- `DOWNLOADING` → show chip, background = `gn_status_downloading` (#1E9FFF), text = "XX%"
- `NOT_INSTALLED` → hide chip entirely (`chip.visibility = GONE`)
- `ERROR` → show chip, background = `gn_status_error` (#FF4D6A), text = "Error"

