## Part 5 — Fragment wiring

In your library fragment (AppListFragment / LibraryScreen / LibraryListPane):

```kotlin
private val adapter = AppListAdapter(
    onGameClick     = { game -> viewModel.launchGame(game) },
    onGameLongClick = { game, anchor -> showGameContextMenu(game, anchor) },
    onFavoriteClick = { game -> viewModel.toggleFavorite(game) }
)

binding.recyclerViewGames.apply {
    layoutManager = GridLayoutManager(requireContext(), 2)
    this.adapter  = this@LibraryFragment.adapter
    setHasFixedSize(false)            // false: title rows vary in height
    setItemViewCacheSize(20)
    setItemPrefetchEnabled(true)
    (layoutManager as GridLayoutManager).initialPrefetchItemCount = 6
}
```

**Always use submitList — never notifyDataSetChanged:**
```kotlin
viewModel.filteredGames.observe(viewLifecycleOwner) { games ->
    adapter.submitList(games)
    binding.layoutEmptyState.isVisible = games.isEmpty()
    binding.recyclerViewGames.isVisible = games.isNotEmpty()
    binding.shimmerLayout.isVisible = false
    binding.shimmerLayout.stopShimmer()
}

viewModel.isLoading.observe(viewLifecycleOwner) { loading ->
    if (loading) {
        binding.shimmerLayout.isVisible = true
        binding.shimmerLayout.startShimmer()
    }
}
```

**Chip filter wiring:**
```kotlin
binding.chipGroupFilters.setOnCheckedStateChangeListener { _, checkedIds ->
    viewModel.setFilter(when (checkedIds.firstOrNull()) {
        R.id.chipInstalled    -> LibraryFilter.INSTALLED
        R.id.chipRecent       -> LibraryFilter.RECENT
        R.id.chipFavorites    -> LibraryFilter.FAVORITES
        R.id.chipNotInstalled -> LibraryFilter.NOT_INSTALLED
        else                  -> LibraryFilter.ALL
    })
}
```

**Grid/list view toggle:**
```kotlin
binding.btnViewToggle.setOnClickListener {
    adapter.displayMode = when (adapter.displayMode) {
        AppListAdapter.DisplayMode.GRID -> {
            binding.recyclerViewGames.layoutManager = LinearLayoutManager(requireContext())
            binding.btnViewToggle.setImageResource(R.drawable.ic_grid_view)
            AppListAdapter.DisplayMode.LIST
        }
        AppListAdapter.DisplayMode.LIST -> {
            binding.recyclerViewGames.layoutManager = GridLayoutManager(requireContext(), 2)
            binding.btnViewToggle.setImageResource(R.drawable.ic_list_view)
            AppListAdapter.DisplayMode.GRID
        }
    }
}
```

**SteamGridDB — fetch 600×900 portrait art, not header:**
```
GET https://www.steamgriddb.com/api/v2/grids/steam/{appId}?dimensions=600x900&type=static
Authorization: Bearer ${STEAMGRIDDB_API_KEY}
```
Cache to: `app_data/artwork/{appId}_capsule.jpg`

Fall-back chain:
1. SteamGridDB 600×900 portrait
2. Steam CDN: `https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/{appId}/library_600x900.jpg`
3. Steam CDN header (`header.jpg`) letterboxed to fit 2:3 card
4. `R.drawable.ic_placeholder_cover`

