## Part 6 — RecyclerView pool sharing

Share a `RecycledViewPool` between the library grid and any search results
fragment so ViewHolders are not recreated when switching tabs:

```kotlin
val sharedPool = RecyclerView.RecycledViewPool().apply {
    setMaxRecycledViews(VIEW_TYPE_GRID, 20)
    setMaxRecycledViews(VIEW_TYPE_LIST, 20)
}
binding.recyclerViewGames.setRecycledViewPool(sharedPool)
```

