## Part 7 — Predictive back (Android 14+)

Replace all `onBackPressed()` overrides with the modern callback:
```kotlin
requireActivity().onBackPressedDispatcher.addCallback(viewLifecycleOwner) {
    // handle back navigation here
}
```
This enables Android 14's swipe-back preview animation (shows the previous
screen behind the current one during the gesture). Makes navigation feel
significantly more polished.
